dct_description_sm: Time Weekly Magazine. North Decimal Degree 43.000000. South Decimal Degree 27.0000. East Decimal Degree 78.0000. West Decimal Degree 19.0000. Relief shown by shading. Pictorial 1950's Cold War map. "Enlarged of original map drawn for Time, the weekly newsmagazine." In lower right margin: "Reprinted from TIME January, 16, 1956.".
